<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='2206' id='t-2206'>I'm a potter,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='5224' id='t-5224'>which seems like a fairly humble vocation.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='9749' id='t-9749'>I know a lot about pots.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='12629' id='t-12629'>I've spent about 15 years making them.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='16309' id='t-16309'>One of the things that really
