<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='42706' id='t-42706'>and I didn't know how to make a foot yet,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='44810' id='t-44810'>I would have to learn how to make a foot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='47829' id='t-47829'>that that process of learning
