</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:10
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='59067' id='t-59067'>There have been times
in my artistic capacity</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='62178' id='t-62178'>that I wanted to reflect</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='65041' id='t-65041'>on other really important moments</span>
