</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:32
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='141607' id='t-141607'>After clay, I was then kind of turned on
