</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 3:09
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='178204' id='t-178204'>The neighborhood that I live in
is Grand Crossing.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='181153' id='t-181153'>It's a neighborhood
