</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:14
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='243085' id='t-243085'>And so I bought a building.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='244733' id='t-244733'>The building was really affordable.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='247473' id='t-247473'>We tricked it out.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='249185' id='t-249185'>We made it as beautiful as we could
