<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='272544' id='t-272544'>It worked out.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='274703' id='t-274703'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='276938' id='t-276938'>But we would use the building, then,
