<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='323440' id='t-323440'>One house turned into a few houses,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='325622' id='t-325622'>and we always tried to suggest</span>
