<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='905649' id='t-905649'>but the other work of a kind
of neighborhood consciousness,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='909016' id='t-909016'>that part doesn't live anymore.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='910990' id='t-910990'>So how do you start to grow up
important watchdogs</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='915796' id='t-915796'>that ensure that the resources
